<p>She went on to add the tag '#lovetheskinyourein.' </p>

<p>The reality TV star went on to share more photos to social media on Thursday, in a bright blue top, with large statement ruffled sleeves. </p>

<p>'The blue is all for you,' she wrote in the caption of a selfie taken in a car, alongside a red heart emoji. </p>

<p>Showing off her full outfit, Kenya posed against a black light post in light wash skinny jeans, white high-heels and a multi-colored snakeskin bag.  </p>

